Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,中_置顶,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.83,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:37.18,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:42.19,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:47.70,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you kill your friends, if you can fulfill your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:50.19,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you die for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.33,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:58.59,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life is a game It's a survival That's right! How do you start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:04.09,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time and Space It's a crossroad through a gate! Where do you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.62,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.78,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need to live
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:13.75,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.03,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.93,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.94,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.81,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:27.32,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:31.97,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:35.02,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.17,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:44.77,op2en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.83,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带刺的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:37.18,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你的故事里认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:42.19,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨之深皆因爱之切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:47.70,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为一己之利置朋友于死地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:50.19,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会为了他人而牺牲自我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.33,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们又有何区别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:58.59,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！人生就是生存游戏　你要如何开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:04.09,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间和空间是分岔路口　你要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.62,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻求永生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.78,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但生存的意义又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:13.75,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不知道世界的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.03,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是时空的乱入者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.93,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不会因你而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.94,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则才决定着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.81,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我们凭着爱穿越古今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:27.32,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:31.97,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:35.02,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.17,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奇迹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:44.77,op2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是终结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:39.69,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:44.81,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動許される?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:55.92,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会いたくて涙 溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:22:01.73,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全ては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:09.35,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩れる身体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:21.79,日_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう一度君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:39.69,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟还要失去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:44.81,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这剧烈的心悸方能被宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:55.92,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要见到你 想到热泪盈眶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:22:01.73,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是连接着未来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:09.35,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到崩坏身体的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:21.79,中_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意 再一次守护你 许下誓言
